address2: 6th Floor No. 728 Yan’an West Road Changning District
longBusinessSummary: ArtGo Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, primarily engages in the mining, processing, trading, and sale of marble stones in the People's Republic of China. It operates in two segments, Marble Products and Others. The company offers marble slabs, standard cut to size marble, antique series, water jet, border series, and marble-related crafts for bathroom and tailor-made household products. It is also involved in the provision of technical services for stone processing; production and sale of calcium carbonate products; warehousing, logistics, and sale of mineral products; and mining investment and mining planting projects; and wholesale and retail of decorating materials and chemical products. The company was formerly known as ArtGo Mining Holdings Limited and changed its name to ArtGo Holdings Limited in March 2015. ArtGo Holdings Limited was founded in 2009 and is headquartered in Shanghai, the People's Republic of China.
